@node items "game items and how to use'em..."

There are so many tools & weapons and i might change them later,
so i can't write perfect instructions to all tools. sorry, you
just have to trie them out and learn :)    (was that bad english??)

but here are a few tips:
------------------------

* bazooka, homer, grenade, supball, freezer & bigchina uses the
  powerbar.  (hold down space and release (just like in worms).)

* jetpack is activated using space. use arrowkeys to control it.
  if you press down arrow it shuts down.

* molebomb is also controlled via arrowkeys.

